{"tid":1100133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為手機爆炸，導致用家嚴重燒傷，網上消息已被官方封鎖","createTime":"2019-04-10T08:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T05:27:37.000Z","uid":155095,"like":287,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"867df646648eeaedeac4907e67075476d5d66cd2","tid":1100133,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:30:20.000Z","msg":"中國網絡消息指，華為手機發生爆炸事故，導致用戶父親大腿嚴重燒傷。北京時間4月10日，中國多家財經網媒報道稱，4月1日，一名叫&ldquo;身體好虎&rdquo;的網友爆料，自己父親放在口袋裡的華為Nova3手機發生爆炸，導致大腿嚴重燒傷。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic4.dwnews.net/20190410/0d5c49520eeae632e7c615864426743c_w_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic4.dwnews.net%2F20190410%2F0d5c49520eeae632e7c615864426743c_w_m.jpg&h=e6b264c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n華為是中國一家高科技企業，在研發通信設備的同時，亦推出手機業務。華為因業務的高光表現，以及受到美國封殺而廣為人知。<br />\n<br />\n 4月1日，華為手機業務官微&ldquo;華為終端客服&rdquo;就回應稱，&ldquo;您的問題正在處理中，還請您耐心等待&rdquo;。 疑似華為手機產品線副總裁李小龍回應稱，自己不了解情況，但問題多出於用戶私自拆機和假冒電池所致。 李小龍還說，華為已推出補貼低價電池，就是想壓縮假冒電池的生存空間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic0.dwnews.net/20190410/4ea00e6c3ed6c22e80144e98bd413be8_w_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic0.dwnews.net%2F20190410%2F4ea00e6c3ed6c22e80144e98bd413be8_w_m.jpg&h=9d304d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於上述爆炸事故，李小龍透露已派專人處理。 不過，目前除一些截圖之外，&ldquo;身體好虎&rdquo;的爆料微博和其他財經媒體的報道均已被刪除，被指受華為公關所致。 <br />\n<br />\n此前，據媒體報道，華為手機內部已確定2019年目標，即趕超韓國企業三星，成為全球最大的智能手機制造廠商。 2018年底，華為常務董事、消費者業務CEO余承東表示，預計2019年華為手機出貨量超2.5億台，2020年將達到3億台。"},{"pid":"c9c598666ebc01ac7e1880af6c287a5be149b30a","tid":1100133,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />高速"},{"pid":"2bbd2ea97626c79911f499de7675ec48c218d6a2","tid":1100133,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785421d3f3c0a60b059c3da54dc69237428d3c26","tid":1100133,"uid":65378,"like":100,"dislike":0,"score":100,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:32:58.000Z","msg":"李小龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14251c5506066c71f70f47abaa404c49d2620e43","tid":1100133,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:33:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb072c49e959e5afb0bee8cd3770af6a2ff16c7","tid":1100133,"uid":14918,"like":110,"dislike":0,"score":110,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"爆炸? 好正常啫。中国喎"},{"pid":"7607748349a655f5a589b431d3ee8d241f4a7eda","tid":1100133,"uid":53577,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:34:16.000Z","msg":"華為遙控爆炸裝置意外起動啫，意外。"},{"pid":"6f421cc9e7a08de9532a0f601295589638823c93","tid":1100133,"uid":27451,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:34:29.000Z","msg":"先進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6c855f9a1ee2c3232ce5869d31c1564ed8bc87","tid":1100133,"uid":25750,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T08:34:5